PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of RENAUD CARON, of Cap-Rouge, Quebec, selected from the public service of Canada, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Federal Business Development Bank to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years; and designation of RENAUD CARON as a director of the Executive Committee of the Federal Business Development Bank, in the place of Lorette Goulet.
Attachments
precis:
Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of RENAUD CARON,
of Cap-Rouge, Quebec, selected from the public service of Canada, as a
director of the Board of Directors of the Federal Business Development
Bank to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years; and
designation of RENAUD CARON as a director of the Executive Committee of
the Federal Business Development Bank, in the place of Lorette Goulet.
